      <title>美联储鲍威尔：猜测政策宽松还为时过早</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-01/fed-s-powell-premature-to-speculate-on-policy-easing-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔在亚特兰大斯佩尔曼学院的一次活动中表示：“我们采取的强有力行动已将我们的政策利率提高到限制性水平。” （来源：斯佩尔曼学院）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-01/fed-s-powell-premature-to-speculate-on-policy-easing-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 16:35:15 GMT</pubDate>
